data.description: This is your perfect home so STOP here and look no further! No HOA, outside the city limits so park your RV (hookups are there), trailer or boat. This beautiful 3 bedroom with 2 baths home also has a 2nd living area that can be used as an office, game room or bedroom. Open concept living, dining and kitchen is perfect for entertaining. The nicely appointed kitchen comes complete with granite counters and backsplash, double ovens, farm sink and walk-in pantry. The floor to ceiling stone fireplace anchors the living space sending a calm and relaxing feel. The huge primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings and the ensuite bath offers dual sinks and granite counters, a soaking tub and separate walk-in shower for TWO (or more:)! The huge walk-in closet also leads to the laundry room with custom cabinets and storage galore! The huge backyard has a built-in fireplace on a cozy covered patio perfect for relaxing. A privacy wood fence surrounds the backyard that is ready for your personal touch.
